{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Plan-review triage (run 2: PASS, 0 blocking, 20 advisory). FIXED by amendment: data-flow into gate machinery pinned — assembled context passes as diff_text through the existing adapter seam, no runner changes (fcb41bff/f1dbb1fd); metric/log names specified — journald events + review_bot_merge_change_errors via observability.sh (f9865424); _TAG_SUFFIXES semantics — reuse existing verdict keys, suffix appended, no new vocabulary (fe71742e/f0f5a950); setup-project.sh want-dict extension named as S1 target for feature-branch-drivers (fcc4cb2e/fe8e7624); extra commit GET on hot path accepted + documented, fails closed (f4a69748); mergelist/any-merge-REST-failure fallback pinned — fail-closed -1 with coverage-gap tag (fb1a8198/fcaeb72c); abandoned/stale-branch inventory policy added to S6 (f4ed4381); merge-conflict + abandon-merge-change guidance added to S4 recipe (fe5968cd); MERGELIST_MAX_COMMITS named constant (f3f52706); bot-code rollback in S6 + runbook (f3523579); per-file diff fan-out bounded by the combined cap (f0122315). JUSTIFIED, not fixed: g2p ini investigation cannot be resolved pre-1fa8 — g2p is not installed; S3 carries the verified-statement done-definition (f0b0d8da); webhook branch-agnosticism is config-confirmed AND live-proven by S5 scenario 1's done-definition (f55167b8); gerrit-verify.yaml intentionally does not exist yet — an explicit 1fa8 dependency assumption stated in Context (fc2ae55d); MERGE_FIRST_PARENT_UPDATE acceptance now pinned to S1 (config push) + S5 scenario 4 (live carry) (f7e29888 — partially fixed); DET compound-criteria style — house epic convention, S-items decompose into child stories with granular ACs (f607dd45, standing justification)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782962808949743001,"uuid":"5f33840c-6f2f-4925-ad16-9c11b103a73c"}